and a healthy respect for the entrepreneurial system.
   When the nation's governors were asked: Who among you is the
most effective leader, the answer was Michael Dukakis of
Massachusetts. When millions of Democrats went to the polls this
year to choose the leader who will blaze America's path during the
21st century, they chose Michael Dukakis of Massachusetts.
   Michael Dukakis has the uncanny knack of bringing forth the very
best in America. He knows that government can't solve all our
problems. But he also understands that government has an obligation
to lead.
