fair; Los Angeles 70 cloudy; Phoenix 94 partly cloudy; Salt Lake
City 70 fair; San Diego 72 partly cloudy; San Francisco 59 partly
cloudy; Seattle 62 fair.
   _Canada: Montreal 66 fair; Toronto 66 fair.
