favor of all of them ...
   ``What was remarkable in the convention was the outstanding
performance of Jesse Jackson. He appears to have decided to
cooperate with Dukakis to unify the party ahead of the November
election, but the fact that the rise of the Rainbow Coalition,
which represents interests of blacks, Hispanics, minority groups
and the low-income class, indicates the emergence of a new flow in
the American society.''
