<HEAD>Flood Death Toll Rises To 12</HEAD>
<DATELINE>TOKYO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The death toll from floods in the Hiroshima area of
western Japan rose to 12 today when rescue workers recovered four
more bodies, police said.
