<HEAD>Guard Robs Bank That Employed Him</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MANILA, Philippines (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A security guard hired to protect a
bank from robbers held up the bank himself, police and bank
officials said Friday.
   Investigators said the guard waited for other guards to leave
the Quezon City branch of the Philippine Commercial and Industrial
Bank as it closed Thursday and made his move just before the
remaining tellers closed the vault.
